From that strategic foundation, the project developed a Vietnamese-facing brand DNA centered on **“The Gentle Caregiver Companion”** and the message **“Nâng niu yêu thương mỗi ngày, từ những điều nhỏ bé nhất”**. The brand was framed not as loud, sales-driven, or overly functional, but as a gentle, refined, dependable presence in daily family life. The tone of voice and visual identity were designed to feel **tinh tế, nhẹ nhàng, tận tâm-**elevating the brand while keeping it accessible and emotionally grounded.
